reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful little flower decoration
reviews.reviewText: I got this for my bathroom and it’s just adorable. You have to arrange the flowers yourself but it’s super easy to make them look. Super cute. It looks very high-end and would match with anything.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 2, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This flower arrangement is very lovely on its own. For the little vase that came with it, I did peel the sticker off and it left behind a gluey residue, so I cannot use it until I get the residue off. Then I plan to possibly paint the vase and then I can use it. Some people might not care and you could turn it around so the sticker is in the back rather than go to all the trouble of removing it. The flowers themselves are really nice and realistic looking. They even feel realistic to the touch. I just need to work on the base a little and then get the flowers arranged properly if I can possibly do that myself and then it should be ready to go.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Cute, but the name sticker will not come off easily
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this to use as a table centerpiece and it is a bit small. The faux flowers and greenery are not set in the vase and can flop around. The name sticker is very difficult to remove. The silk flowers and plastic greenery are pretty good quality and better than I have seen at other retailer. Overall it is cute, and probably worth the $15.99 price tag, based on the cost of faux greenery and flowers elsewhere. It is not quite as large as pictured, but close. It really needs some acrylic water or vase beads to stabilize the stems.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 19, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the YXZZWL Artificial Flowers with Vase and I must say that I am thoroughly impressed! The attention to detail on each individual rose and eucalyptus leaf is stunning and the addition of the faux berries really brings the arrangement to life. The vase itself is also of high quality and adds a touch of elegance to any space.I have placed the arrangement on my coffee table in my living room and it has become a real conversation piece. Guests are always amazed when they find out that they are not real flowers! The white color of the roses adds a sense of purity and freshness to my space.What I love most about this product is its versatility. It can be used as a centerpiece on a dining table, as a decoration in an office, or even as farmhouse decor. I have even placed it in my kitchen to add a touch of beauty to my cooking space.Overall, I highly recommend the YXZZWL Artificial Flowers with Vase to anyone looking for a beautiful and long-lasting floral arrangement for their home. It is a true work of art and I am so happy to have it in my space!
